item.title: My First Flute Performance
item.description: Date: 2013 Location: Lakeside Lutheran Piece: Composer: somebody Accompanist: This was my first flute performance ever! I was in 5th grade, studying under Peter Ziegler at the time. I was really nervous for this performance because the room was filled with many people, who likely were waiting for the next performer. In the end I bowed because I didn’t know what else to do!
